Name: Hkons Beanrunner
About the game: parkour trough obstacles and try to get to the end as fast as possible or try to find the hidden coins as fast as possible. there is also a maze u have to get trough, but the maze might move alittlebit while u are in there. try to get an insane speedrun by using both the forward and sideways button to get even more speed. in the game u might die of something stupid like a fake floor or something btw XD. there also are enemys but im sure u can outsmart them and even use one of them. its alittle frustrating btw hehehe
